## ๐พ 2. ููู `register.php`

```php
<?php
$conn = new mysqli("localhost", "root", "", "my_database");

$username = $_POST['username'];
$email = $_POST['email'];
$password = $_POST['password']; // ูู ุงููุดุงุฑูุน ุงูุญููููุฉ ูุฌุจ ุชุดููุฑ ูููุฉ ุงูุณุฑ

